  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer Note</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was created as a passion project by a solo indie developer.<br><strong>Development is no longer active</strong>, and the game is provided <i>as-is</i> for those who wish to experience it or explore the early work of the developer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your understanding — and for supporting indie games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010340/extras/61fee28eff0cab4d669603b3537cb4fb.avif?t=1759607360\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Indie fighting game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game contains 3 game methods</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1- Chapters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010340/extras/102c922f75a70c11caffcfad7c21a66e.avif?t=1759607360\" width=540 height=304 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2- Local multiplayer (3D)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010340/extras/d61285ae624da8057bad9f28aa70b751.avif?t=1759607360\" width=400 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3- Online ( 3D )</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Online mode, you are going to face a real person and fight them to get more and more ranks to open your mission and get EXP to build your own character and make him stronger, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>there are 5 Ranks in the game for each rank you are going to get EXP to build your ability,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010340/extras/0881fd8e8f2245dc0939475e15b9f09f.avif?t=1759607360\" width=400 height=226 /></span><u>for each win, you are going to get 2 points</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>if you lost the game, you are going to lose 2 points</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >if you faced any problems, please send an email to <a href=\"mailto:(skullsameh.work@gmail.com)\">(skullsameh.work@gmail.com)</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >enjoy</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer Note</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was created as a passion project by a solo indie developer.<br><strong>Development is no longer active</strong>, and the game is provided <i>as-is</i> for those who wish to experience it or explore the early work of the developer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your understanding — and for supporting indie games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010340/extras/61fee28eff0cab4d669603b3537cb4fb.avif?t=1759607360\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Indie fighting game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game contains 3 game methods</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1- Chapters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010340/extras/102c922f75a70c11caffcfad7c21a66e.avif?t=1759607360\" width=540 height=304 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2- Local multiplayer (3D)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010340/extras/d61285ae624da8057bad9f28aa70b751.avif?t=1759607360\" width=400 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3- Online ( 3D )</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Online mode, you are going to face a real person and fight them to get more and more ranks to open your mission and get EXP to build your own character and make him stronger, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>there are 5 Ranks in the game for each rank you are going to get EXP to build your ability,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010340/extras/0881fd8e8f2245dc0939475e15b9f09f.avif?t=1759607360\" width=400 height=226 /></span><u>for each win, you are going to get 2 points</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>if you lost the game, you are going to lose 2 points</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >if you faced any problems, please send an email to <a href=\"mailto:(skullsameh.work@gmail.com)\">(skullsameh.work@gmail.com)</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >enjoy</p>",
